summary: SummaryHighlightsClean IngredientsVeganGive BackMaybelline Super Stay Matte Ink Liquid Lipstick creates a flawless, high-pigment matte finish with up to 16 hours of wear.
details: DetailsBenefitsSmooth matte finish lasts all dayFeatures a unique arrow tip that provides a precise applicationAvailable in a range of rich, saturated shadesItem 2510218How To UseStep 1: Apply lipstick in the center of your upper lip and follow the contours of your mouth.Step 2: Glide the lipstick across the entire bottom lip.Precautions: Flammable until dry. Do not use near fire, flame, or heat.IngredientsDimethicone, Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Isododecane, Nylon-611 / Dimethicone Copolymer, Dimethicone Crosspolymer, C30-45 Alkyldimethylsilyl Polypropylsilsesquioxane, Lauroyl Lysine, Alumina, Silica Silylate, Disodium Stearoyl Glutamate, Phenoxyethanol, Caprylyl Glycol, Limonene, Aluminum Hydroxide, Paraffin, Benzyl Benzoate, Benzyl Alcohol, Citronellol, Parfum / Fragrance. May Contain: CI 45410 / Red 28 Lake, CI 77891 / Titanium Dioxide, CI 15850 / Red 7, CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499 / Iron Oxides, CI 45380 / Red 22 Lake, CI 15985 / Yellow 6 Lake, CI 19140 / Yellow 5 Lake, CI 42090 / Blue 1 Lake, CI 15850 / Red 6, CI 17200 / Red 33 Lake, Mica.
how_to_use: Step 1: Apply lipstick in the center of your upper lip and follow the contours of your mouth.Step 2: Glide the lipstick across the entire bottom lip.Precautions: Flammable until dry. Do not use near fire, flame, or heat.

reviews.headline: I would buy again all the diff shades
reviews.comments: It's amazing buttery and super staying lipstick. amazing quality in this price ðŸ¤©

reviews.headline: Not my fav lippie!
reviews.comments: As much as I love a transfer proof lip product which this does indeed, it's too thick and sticky. It feels heavy almost. If you need a lip product that won't move than this is for you, if you don't mind reapplying then this is a no! The color variation is amazing.

reviews.headline: Long Lasting!
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I love this matte lip gloss! The color was a little darker than I typically wear but still looked great. It stayed on all day and didn't smudge at all.

reviews.headline: Formula has been consistent
reviews.comments: Long lasting. I like the colors available. I bought this a few years ago, and the formula has stayed consistent in terms of feel and how long the lipstick lasts.

reviews.headline: Long lasting!
reviews.comments: I've tried MANY  liquid lipsticks and this one takes the cake for being the most long lasting. I can wear this all day and eat several meals and to still holds up. My only complaint is it feels a little sticky, but you get used to it.

reviews.headline: This lipstick did not budge!
reviews.comments: I wore this SuperStay Matte Ink Liquid Lipstick on my wedding day. Applied at 10am. Wedding at 1pm. Reception at 3. I did a tiny touchup before the reception and nothing else for the remainder of the day. The lipstick was still going strong at 10pm. This lipstick did NOT budge. I'd absolutely recommend this to anyone Good stuff!!

reviews.headline: Great stay
reviews.comments: Have previously purchased other colors in this and love them all. They last most the day and still look good pretty smudge proof a well

reviews.headline: Will NOT come off
reviews.comments: This is my favorite lipstick ever I put it on at 7:30 yesterday morning and had to use my make up remover two times to get it off last night at 10:15!

reviews.headline: Long lasting!
reviews.comments: I do not wear lipstick often because I'm not good at keeping it on throughout a night, but with this I don't have to worry! It stays a looong time and is even kinda hard to get off. I need a better makeup remover. Great color as well.

reviews.headline: If you like sticky
reviews.comments: I love love love the color, but after it "drys" its still a little sticky. So far its staying but im a little nervous about the color stay

reviews.headline: I definitely will buy this product again!
reviews.comments: I highly recommend this matte lipstick

reviews.headline: Lasts all day!
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] Maybelline Super Stay Matte Ink is one of the best long-wear liquid lipsticks out there. The pigment is rich, bold, and goes on smooth with just one swipe. Once it sets, it really locks inâ€”no smudging, fading, or transferring, even after eating and drinking. The matte finish looks flawless without drying out the lips, and the applicator makes it easy to get clean lines. Affordable, reliable, and perfect if you need a lipstick that truly lasts all day.

reviews.headline: Never comes off on my teeth
reviews.comments: I am one who wears dentures and this formula is matte and stays on my lips without coming off on my dentures. My daughter wears it also and it does not come off on your teeth. The color is beautiful. The stay  is long lasting and every time I run out of it, I run out and buy more. I keep one in my purse and one in my makeup drawer I will never be without this.

reviews.headline: Finally, a color that lasts ALL Day.
reviews.comments:
By far, this is the best lip stain that stays on the entire day.  This is a great product, nice colors, I do wish they had a bigger color selection. 
Highly recommend.

reviews.headline: 10/10 absolutely recommend
reviews.comments: So, I don't usually do reviews as much as i should but i HAD to do one for this product. I got the shade Thrill Seeker for an upcoming concert. I am incredibly impressed with the quality of this matte black. I wore it early to test it and the wear was so long lasting, it survived 8 hours with minimal color diminishing including through eating, drinking, and rubbing my lips to ensure it wouldn't smudge. Believe the hype. For the price and quality/pigment/applicator you cannot beat this. Its the best matte black I have ever tried!!!

reviews.headline: I would buy this product again
reviews.comments: I've rebought this item because I like the way it works and doesn't smear off

reviews.headline: The perfect lipstick
reviews.comments: I said it! This is it folks. The perfect liquid matte lipstick. I have this in so many colors- my favorites being self starter, and seductress!!

reviews.headline: I will buy this product again!
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I absolutely love this product! The application is super simple and easy-to-use. The pigment is abscond and lasts so long! I don't even need to take it with me on date night because I don't even need to reapply. My husband also loves that he doesn't have to worry about transfer when I kiss him!

reviews.headline: Daily use
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] These matte lipsticks go on smooth and don't feel super drying but truly are amazing at not coming off. I put this on and add a clear gloss. If your into night activities, this is the one for you!

reviews.headline: Buying all the shades!
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I have tried Maybelline lip products before. But this one is my favorite! It literally stays on no transfer at all! The color is so pretty. I like the look of the packaging as well.

faceoff_positive.comments:
I received both pioneer and lover for free to review from influenster and this is what I have to say about them.. 

Packaging: sleek and simple , love the wand you can be precise and also the hole in the center packs extra for main filling. The wand gives you good control.

The color of PIONEER is like that of a red rose to me and i love that i can see the violet undertones.. i will definitely be purchasing patriot again and some of the more deeper shades.

LOVER is subtle and pretty , it has a nice color and isn't too bright or too dark for my skin type, good pink.

Both LOVER AND PIONEER have a matte finish as advertised.

Advise: You only need to apply once, i don't recommend applying twice
the texture is a little sticky but not so much that i can't handle it.

I have ate burgers with these lipsticks and they hold up great.
only time i noticed a good difference is when i ate an overly greasy pizza 

The lippies are removed with oil, i personally choose coconut oil and it does it's job, i would say don't skimp out on your oil, use a good amount and removing it shouldn't be a problem.

Cons/ It could be a tiny bit less tacky and i'm sure if they had more of a selection of shades they would be even more popular.

I am excited to try more of the deeper shades soon :)
faceoff_positive.headline: could be slightly perfected but i will still buy
